Cp%3EMonty%20Rakusen%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFOBO%20was%20the%20new%20buzzword%20floating%20around%20Davos%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20term%20represents%20employees'%20fears%20of%20being%20made%20obsolete%20by%20AI%20advances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReverse%20mentoring%20and%20targeted%20upskilling%20can%20help%20employees%20stay%20relevant%2C%20business%20leaders%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERapid%20AI%20advances%20present%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-using-ai-bain-survey-roi-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealluring%20opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20businesses%20to%20boost%20productivity%20and%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20CEOs%20battle%20their%20FOMO%20and%20race%20to%20adopt%20the%20new%20technology%2C%20their%20employees%20are%20experiencing%20a%20different%20side%20of%20the%20AI%20revolution%20%E2%80%94%20FOBO%2C%20the%20fear%20of%20becoming%20obsolete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20refers%20to%20workers'%20fears%20that%20the%20speed%20of%20AI%20development%20is%20outpacing%20the%20reskilling%20of%20employees%2C%20leaving%20them%20redundant%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fworkplace%2F609320%2Fno-fear-obsolete-upskilling-revolution.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGallup%3C%2Fa%3E%20polling%2C%20FOBO%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%C2%A022%25%20of%20US%20workers%20surveyed%20said%20they%20were%20worried%20their%20jobs%20would%20become%20obsolete%20because%20of%20technology%2C%20up%20from%2015%25%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFOBO%20was%20a%20buzzword%20that%20kept%20popping%20up%20around%20this%20year's%20Davos%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20panel%20titled%20%26quot%3BClosing%20the%20Jobs%20Gap%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-crisis-singapore-president-davos-wef-unemployment-ai-education-work-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESingapore's%20president%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Tharman%20Shanmugaratnam%2C%20warned%20that%20a%20global%20jobs%20crisis%20is%20looming%20and%20called%20for%20governments%20and%20employers%20to%20continually%20invest%20in%20workers%20to%20increase%20the%20chances%20that%20AI%20complements%20their%20skills%20instead%20of%20rendering%20them%20obsolete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20leaders%20should%20be%20just%20as%20interested%20in%20doubling%20down%20on%20upskilling%20initiatives%20as%20they%20are%20purchasing%20the%20latest%20AI%20tools%2C%20Ravin%20Jesuthasan%2C%20a%20renowned%20future-of-work%20expert%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Skills-Powered%20Organization%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20ROI%20incentive%20to%20ensure%20their%20workers%20don't%20get%20left%20behind%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20giving%20people%20access%20to%20Chat%20GPT%2C%20won't%20get%20you%20a%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jesuthasan.%20Adoption%20rates%20tend%20to%20be%20low%20when%20workers%20are%20just%20handed%20a%20tool%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20companies%20should%20make%20all%20training%20mandatory%20and%20set%20aside%20time%20for%20learning%20during%20the%20working%20day%20to%20encourage%20engagement%2C%20Jesuthasan%20said.%20But%20they%20should%20also%20be%20strategic%20in%20how%20they%20train%20the%20workforce%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20you%20really%20get%20the%20ROI%20is%20by%20identifying%20exactly%20what%20work%20is%20going%20to%20be%20substituted%20by%20AI%2C%20Jesuthasan%20explained.%20Employers%20can%20then%20take%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20freed%20up%2C%20assess%20what%20new%20skills%20they%20need%2C%20and%20retrain%20and%20deploy%20them%20with%20those%20skills%20to%20drive%20more%20growth%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERafee%20Tarafdar%2C%20Chief%20Technology%20Officer%20of%20Infosys%2C%20the%20Indian%20tech%20giant%2C%20also%20said%20that%20his%20company%20was%20seeing%20great%20success%20with%20its%20in-house%20learning%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInfosys%20has%20updated%20the%20system%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-leaders-share-how-they-integrated-ai-company-pilot-use-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20AI%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20created%20an%20incentive%20program%20that%20rewards%20employees%20when%20they%20complete%20modules.%20Employees%20are%20spending%20an%20average%20of%2030%20minutes%20a%20day%20learning%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform's%20on-the-go%20nature%20was%20a%20big%20draw%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20an%20employee%20wants%20to%20learn%20anytime%2C%20anywhere%2C%20on%20any%20device%2C%20they%20should%20have%20access%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarafdar%20also%20agreed%20that%20differentiating%20employees%20based%20on%20how%20they'll%20use%20AI%20was%20key%20to%20upskilling%20them%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20some%20of%20them%20will%20be%20consumers%20of%20AI%2C%20which%20means%20they%20will%20use%20the%20AI%20tools%20in%20order%20to%20become%20more%20productive%20and%20efficient%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20will%20be%20creators%20of%20AI.%20And%20then%20somewhere%20in%20between%2C%20we'll%20have%20builders%2C%20those%20whose%20skills%20will%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20by%20developing%20courses%20in%20such%20a%20focused%20way%2C%20each%20employee%20is%20learning%20how%20to%20drive%20value%20for%20their%20specific%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c990760-b1e0-4182-9bb8-9e1c9994fa34%5C%22%3EReverse%20mentoring%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFOBO%20could%20be%20a%20particular%20problem%20among%20more%20senior%20workers%2C%20Jesuthasan%20said.%20They%20might%20delegate%20tasks%20to%20a%20secretary%20or%20team%20rather%20than%20AI%2C%20and%20may%20not%20have%20received%20any%20significant%20technical%20training%20for%2020%20years%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20approach%20Jesuthasan%20thinks%20will%20be%20effective%20in%20bridging%20the%20age%20gap%20is%20%26quot%3Breverse%20mentoring%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20more%20mature%20workers%20partner%20up%20with%20younger%20folks%20who%20may%20be%20more%20adept%20with%20modern%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20older%20and%20younger%20worker%20look%20at%20a%20handheld%20screen%20together%20in%20a%20warehouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679391cd2fcded5e90749414%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYounger%20workers%20can%20help%20their%20older%20colleagues%20upskill%2C%20Jesuthasan%20said.%3Cp%3EFG%20Trade%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20digital%20skills%2C%20Jesuthasan%20said.%20Younger%20generations%20also%20have%20transversal%20skills%20and%20a%20different%20worldview%20that%20will%20become%20more%20useful%20in%20the%20AI%20future%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20more%20adept%20because%20they've%20grown%20up%20in%20a%20much%20more%20volatile%20world.%20They've%20not%20had%20the%20luxury%20of%20saying%2C%20I'll%20be%20an%20engineer%20for%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jesuthasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20though%2C%20individuals%20have%20to%20motivate%20themselves%20to%20avoid%20becoming%20redundant%2C%20the%20future-of-work%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20one%20of%20us%20has%20to%20really%20force%20ourselves%20to%20be%20curious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20company%20can%20provide%20resources%2C%20the%20company%20can%20provide%20the%20space%20for%20re-skilling%20and%20upskilling%2C%20but%20the%20individual%20really%20has%20to%20bring%20the%20impetus%20for%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus