20End%20Poverty.%20BJP%20Replies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20BJP%20leaders%20race%20to%20take%20the%20holy%20dip%20during%20the%20Mahakumbh%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20taken%20a%20swipe.%20At%20the%20'Jai%20Bapu%2C%20Jai%20Bhim%2C%20Jai%20Samvidhan'%20rally%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Mhow%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20BJP%20leaders%20kept%20taking%20dips%20for%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president%20questioned%20if%20taking%20dips%20into%20the%20Ganga%20would%20end%20poverty%20in%20the%20country%20or%20fill%20hungry%20stomachs.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20question%20anyone's%20'aastha%20(faith)'.%20If%20anyone%20feels%20bad%2C%20I%20apologise.%20But%20tell%20me%2C%20when%20a%20child%20is%20dying%20of%20hunger%2C%20is%20not%20going%20to%20school%2C%20labourers%20are%20not%20getting%20their%20dues%2C%20at%20such%20a%20time%2C%20these%20people%20are%20spending%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20and%20competing%20for%20taking%20dips%20(in%20the%20Ganga)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20dips%20continue%20till%20it%20appears%20good%20in%20photographs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20people%20cannot%20benefit%20the%20country.%20Our%20faith%20is%20in%20God%20--%20people%20perform%20'puja'%20at%20home%20every%20day%2C%20all%20women%20step%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20after%20performing%20'puja'%2C%20there%20is%20no%20issue.%20But%20we%20have%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20poor%20being%20exploited%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20on%20a%20day%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20took%20a%20holy%20dip%20at%20the%20Triveni%20Sangam%20in%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president's%20remarks%20have%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20BJP.%20Party%20MP%20and%20spokesperson%20Sambit%20Patra%20said%20the%20Congress's%20hatred%20was%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20faith%20of%20crores%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMahakumbh%20has%20been%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20Sanatana%20faith%20for%20ages.%20I%20am%20pained%20to%20say%20that%20while%20the%20entire%20world%20reveres%20this%20faith%2C%20the%20biggest%20opposition%20party%20in%20India%20is%20ridiculing%20the%20Mahakumbh%20and%20this%20faith.%20They%20are%20making%20a%20mockery%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patra%20said%20the%20Congress%20president's%20remarks%20on%20the%20Mahakumbh%20and%20Ganga%20have%20hurt%20crores.%20%26quot%3BHe%20questioned%20if%20taking%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga%20would%20remove%20poverty%2C%20provide%20jobs%2C%20or%20bring%20happiness%20to%20the%20people.%20I%20challenge%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20make%20such%20remarks%20about%20any%20other%20religion's%20faith.%20Can%20they%20question%20if%20people%20get%20jobs%20or%20if%20poverty%20is%20alleviated%20by%20going%20to%20an%20Iftaar%20party%3F%20They%20cannot%20even%20imagine%20toying%20with%20the%20faith%20of%20any%20other%20religion.%20Such%20remarks%20are%20shameful.%20How%20can%20the%20Congress%20have%20such%20anti-Sanatan%20mindset%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737977580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Funa360b8_m-kharge_625x300_27_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-mahakumbh-m-kharge-asks-if-ganga-dips-during-mahakumbh-would-end-poverty-bjp-replies-7570973%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20BJP%20leaders%20race%20to%20take%20the%20holy%20dip%20during%20the%20Mahakumbh%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20taken%20a%20swipe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findi