src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6796a5597bb3f854015a6b2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22823%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMitesh%20Agrawal%20has%20moved%20on%20from%20Lambda%20Labs%20for%20Positron%2C%20a%20new%20player%20in%20the%20AI%20hardware%20space.%3Cp%3EKavita%20Agrawal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELambda%20Labs%20COO%20Mitesh%20Agrawal%20has%20left%20to%20head%20AI%20hardware%20startup%20Positron.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELambda%20focuses%20on%20deploying%20cloud%20infrastructure%20to%20customers%20and%20is%20valued%20at%20over%20%242%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPositron%20aims%20to%20compete%20with%20Nvidia%20by%20offering%20faster%2C%20energy-efficient%20AI%20hardware.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELambda%20Labs%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-new-products-partnerships-gpu-toyota-laptop-geforce-cards-autonomous-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20partner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20lost%20its%20chief%20operating%20officer%20to%20a%20little-known%20company%20building%20hardware%20for%20the%20AI%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELambda%20COO%20Mitesh%20Agrawal%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20stepped%20into%20a%20new%20role%20as%20CEO%20of%20Positron%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Positron%20builds%20hardware%20for%20transformer%20model%20inference%2C%20which%20is%20how%20chatbots%20like%20ChatGPT%20respond%20to%20user%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgrawal's%20departure%20is%20significant%20given%20his%20role%20in%20shaping%20Lambda%20into%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-rapid-funding-rounds-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley's%20best-funded%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20most%20valuable%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20Series%20C%20round%20last%20February%2C%20the%20company%20was%20valued%20at%20about%20%241.5%20billion.%20Agrawal%20declined%20to%20share%20the%20company's%20exact%20valuation%20but%20said%20it%20has%20grown%20to%20over%20%242%20billion%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgrawal%20told%20BI%20that%20when%20he%20joined%20Lambda%20in%202017%2C%20the%20company%20was%20focused%20on%20building%20machines%20for%20image%20generation%20models.%20This%20was%20five%20years%20after%20twin%20brothers%20Stephen%20and%20Michael%20Balaban%20founded%20it%20as%20a%20company%20developing%20facial%20recognition%20technology.%20It%20wasn't%20long%20after%20Agrawal's%20arrival%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20company%20shifted%20its%20focus%2C%20designing%20infrastructure%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-google-microsoft-ai-future-data-centers-monopoly-tech-industry-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-scale%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20pivoting%20into%20cloud%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Lambda's%20business%20now%20focuses%20on%20deploying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-cloud-computing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20customers%2C%20renting%20out%20servers%20powered%20by%20Nvidia's%20graphics%20processing%20units.%20It%20also%20offers%20the%20requisite%20software%2C%20including%20APIs%20for%20inference%20and%20machine%20learning%20libraries%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgrawal%20said%20that%20his%20move%20to%20Positron%20comes%20amid%20a%20growing%20appetite%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-players-startups-ai-inference-driving-prices-down-cheap-workload-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einference%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20capacity%20for%20AI%20models%20to%20apply%20their%20training%20to%20new%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20chatbots%20like%20ChatGPT%20and%20xAI's%20Grok%2C%20and%20new%20reasoning%20models%20like%20OpenAI's%20o1%20tackling%20PhD-level%20problems%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20curve%20of%20technology%20for%20inference%20is%20just%20going%20up%2C%20which%20means%20the%20computational%20requirement%20is%20really%20going%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Agrawal%20said.%20So%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20thinking%20a%20lot%20about%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20solve%20and%20how%20to%20run%20these%20models%20with%20as%20much%20efficiency%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20Positron%20is%20well-positioned%20to%20take%20on%20that%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPositron%20was%20founded%20in%202023%20by%20Thomas%20Sohmers%2C%20whom%20Agrawal%20met%20in%202015.%20The%20two%20also%20overlapped%20at%20Lambda%20during%20Sohmers's%20stint%20at%20the%20company%20between%202020%20and%202021.%20Sohmers%2C%20who%20will%20move%20into%20the%20role%20of%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20told%20BI%20that%2C%20in%20simplest%20terms%2C%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bbuilding%20hardware%20competing%20against%20Nvidia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPositron%20says%20its%20hardware%20outperforms%20Nvidia's%20H100%20and%20H200%20GPUs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20fueled%20the%20AI%20race%20before%20it%20released%20its%20more%20powerful%20Blackwell%20chips%20%E2%80%94%20in%20performance%2C%20power%2C%20and%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20up%20against%20a%20behemoth%20like%20Nvidia%20%E2%80%94%20which%20overtook%20Apple%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20last%20week%20%E2%80%94%20is%20no%20easy%20task%20for%20an%20up-and-coming%20company.%20But%20by%20focusing%20more%20narrowly%20on%20providing%20hardware%20for%20transformer%20model%20inference%2C%20Sohmers%20said%20Positron%20can%20differentiate%20itself%20from%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransformer%20models%20%E2%80%94%20neural%20networks%20that%20learn%20the%20context%20and%20meaning%20of%20data%20to%20generate%20new%20data%20%E2%80%94%20are%20behind%20some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20generative%20AI%20applications.%20Unlike%20convolutional%20neural%20networks%2C%20which%20underpinned%20previous%20decades%20of%20machine%20learning%20advances%2C%20transformer%20models%20have%20greater%20memory%20demands.%20Sohmers%20said%20he%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20capitalize%20on%20those%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20the%20whole%20reason%20we%20started%20Positron%20is%20we%20thought%20that%20there%20was%20a%20better%20way%20to%20do%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Sohmers%20said.%20%26quot%3BNvidia%2C%20as%20a%20large%20company%20that%20also%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20product%20focuses%20wasn't%20going%20to%20really%20optimize%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20particular%20niche%20that%20we're%20focused%20on%2C%20which%20is%20transformer%20model%20inference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgrawal%2C%20too%2C%20is%20confident%20in%20the%20performance%20and%20energy%20efficiency%20of%20Positron's%20hardware.%20Its%20compatibility%20with%20a%20range%20of%20transformer%20models%20will%20also%20help%20it%20attract%20customers%20from%20competitors%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%20has%20such%20a%20strong%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20world%20of%20AI%20models.%20You%20hear%20about%20their%20CUDA%20moat%2C%20and%20you%20heard%20about%20the%20software%20moat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20software%20network%20the%20company%20has%20built%20between%20its%20products%20to%20retain%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Positron%20really%20did%20was%20completely%20remove%20this%20friction%20of%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Agrawal%20said.%20That%20means%20a%20company%20can%20take%20a%20model%20trained%20on%20an%20Nvidia%20GPU%20and%20%26quot%3Brun%20that%20model's%20inference%20on%20a%20Positron%20card%20just%20like%20you%20would%20run%20on%20an%20Nvidia%20GPU%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgrawal%20said%20the%20jump%20from%20an%20established%20player%20like%20Lambda%20to%20a%20young%20startup%20like%20Positron%20presents%20an%20%26quot%3Bexciting%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20to%20compete%20against%20an%20industry%20veteran%20as%20well%20as%20in