0while%20bowling%20357%20overs%20in%2013%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2014.92%20in%202024.%20Bumrah's%2071%20scalps%20in%202024%20made%20him%20just%20the%20fourth%20India%20bowler%20to%20take%20more%20than%2070%20Test%20wickets%20in%20a%20calendar%20year%20after%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20Anil%20Kumble%20and%20Kapil%20Dev.%20Those%20numbers%20were%20enough%20for%20him%20to%20beat%20competition%20from%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Kamindu%20Mendis%20and%20England%20batting%20duo%20of%20Harry%20Brook%2C%20and%20Joe%20Root%20to%20win%20the%20prestigious%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20year%20where%20Bumrah%20excelled%20in%20both%20home%20and%20away%20conditions%2C%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20key%20contributor%20in%20keeping%20India%20in%20contention%20for%20a%20spot%20in%20the%202025%20World%20Test%20Championship%20Final%2C%20though%20the%20side%20fell%20short%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20title%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah's%20incredible%202024%20began%20during%20India's%20memorable%20Test%20win%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20Cape%20Town%2C%20where%20he%20picked%20eight%20wickets.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20bag%2019%20wickets%20in%20India%20beating%20England%204-1%20margin%2C%20with%20the%20highlight%20being%20a%20match%20haul%20of%20nine%20wickets%20and%20helping%20India%20to%20a%20series-levelling%20win%20in%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah's%20most%20standout%20performance%20in%20Tests%20in%202024%20came%20in%20the%20high-stakes%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20Series%20in%20Australia%2C%20where%20he%20picked%2032%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2013.06%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%2028.37%20to%20clinch%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Series%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20series%20in%20Australia%20that%20Bumrah%20crossed%20the%20200%20Test%20wickets%20milestone%2C%20becoming%20the%2012th%20Indian%20bowler%20to%20do%20so%2C%20though%20it%20didn't%20help%20the%20visitors%20in%20avoiding%20a%203-1%