erally%20more%20flexible%20about%20where%20they%20can%20work%20than%20stockpickers%20who%20want%20to%20hear%20directly%20from%20CEOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20young%20analysts%20working%20for%20portfolio%20managers%20based%20in%20Connecticut%20offices%20often%20reverse%20commute%20from%20New%20York%20to%20places%20like%20Greenwich%20or%20Stamford%20so%20they%20can%20still%20enjoy%20the%20nightlife%20and%20culture%20of%20the%20Big%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20talent%20war%20for%20top-shelf%20PMs%20means%20funds%20are%20generally%20more%20flexible%20on%20location%2C%20said%20Vikram%20Tandon%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Durlston%20Partners%20US%2C%20a%20recruiting%20firm.%20But%20that%20flexibility%20has%20a%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20people%20who%20demand%20to%20be%20somewhere%20and%20get%20it%20are%20the%20senior%20people%20who%20are%20setting%20up%20a%20whole%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Tandon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20to%20say%20Florida%20isn't%20on%20the%20rise.%20Data%20from%20hedge-fund%20seeder%20Borealis%20Strategic%20Partners%20shows%20that%2011%25%20of%20US%20hedge%20fund%20launches%20in%202024%20were%20in%20Florida%2C%20compared%20to%20just%203%25%20in%202020.%20The%20Tri-State%20area%20was%20at%2052%25%2C%20down%20from%2056%25%20the%20year%20prior%2C%20according%20to%20Borealis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20portfolio%20managers%20who%20moved%20to%20Miami%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-transforming-palm-beach-winter-white-house-party-economy-maralago-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWest%20Palm%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20for%20two%20different%20multimanagers%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20been%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20them%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20one%20of%20these%20PMs%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20a%20two-hour%20flight%20back%20to%20New%20York.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%