ef%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohn-sculley-interview-healthcare-pepsi-apple-steve-jobs-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohn%20Sculley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20Apple%20CEO%2C%20and%20I%20were%20running%20XL%20Marketing%20Corp%2C%20the%20predecessor%20to%20Zeta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20that%20we%20would%20discard%20every%20platform%20we%20bought%20and%20design%20something%20new.%20We%20took%20400%20of%20our%20500%20full-time%20engineers%20and%20spent%20the%20next%20three%20years%20architecting%20a%20new%20platform%20that%20made%20AI%20and%20data%20native%20to%20the%20application%20layer.%20This%20removed%20all%20the%20legacy%20and%20latency%2C%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20our%20platform's%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20triangulating%2C%20I%20realized%20we%20had%20a%20great%20business%20but%20a%20bad%20model.%20I%20believed%20in%20two%20points%20%E2%80%94%20the%20intersection%20of%20data%20cloud%20and%20marketing%20cloud%20%E2%80%94%20of%20our%20business%2C%20but%20we%20needed%20a%20third%2C%20which%20was%20building%20a%20new%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20calculated%20bet%2C%20and%20I%20convinced%20our%20private%20equity%20partners%20to%20say%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226db097d9-5635-45f8-9713-95e61856abcd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Take%20in%20as%20much%20information%20as%20you%20can%20before%20you%20make%20any%20bets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConsult%20with%20as%20many%20smart%20people%20as%20possible%20before%20you%20make%20a%20big%20move%2C%20and%20create%20the%20highest%20upside%20with%20the%20lowest%20possible%20downside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20become%20comfortable%20with%20making%20less%20money%20for%20a%20few%20years.%20If%20I%20was%20wrong%20about%20referring%20to%20AI%20at%20the%20core%2C%20we%20could%20return%20to%20the%20old%20way.%20If%20I%20was%20right%2C%20which%20I%20was%2C%20it%20was%20a%20step%20function%20change%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20we%20would%20be%20