Muslim).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20waqf%20councils%2C%20whether%20at%20state%20or%20pan-India%20levels%2C%20will%20have%20at%20least%20two%2C%20and%20possibly%20more%20(if%20the%20nominated%20ex-officio%20members%20are%20also%20not%20Muslim)%20members%20not%20from%20the%20Islamic%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20change%20is%20directing%20an%20officer%20nominated%20by%20the%20concerned%20state%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20property%20is%20'waqf'.%20In%20the%20original%20draft%20this%20decision%20was%20left%20to%20the%20District%20Collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20change%20is%20establishing%20that%20the%20law%20will%20not%20apply%20retrospectively%2C%20so%20long%20as%20the%20property%20in%20question%20is%20already%20registered.%20To%20this%20point%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20JPC%20member%20Imran%20Masood%20raised%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20noting%20an%20estimated%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20waqf%20properties%20are%20not%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-cleared-by-joint-parliamentary-committee-14-amendments-approved-7569242%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20Cleared%20By%20JPC%2C%2014%20Amendments%20Approved%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20changes%2C%20and%20the%2011%20others%2C%20were%20proposed%20by%20members%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20including%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20and%20Aparajita%20Sarangi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%2011%20is%20a%20change%20-%20put%20forward%20by%20Mr%20Surya%20-%20specifying%20that%20anybody%20wishing%20to%20donate%20land%20must%20%26quot%3Bshow%20or%20demonstrate%20that%20she%2Fhe%20is%20practicing%20Islam%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20acknowledge%20%26quot%3B...there%20is%20no%20contrivance%20involved%20in%20the%20dedication%20of%20such%20property%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20MPs%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20those%20allied%20to%20it%20made%2023%20proposals%20to%20alter%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill.%20MPs%20from%20the%20opposition%20made%2044%20proposals%2C%20none%20of%20which%20were%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-act-amendment-explainer-women-non-muslims-on-boards-council-cant-claim-land-waqf-act-changes-6282656%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%2C%20Non-Muslims%2C%20Council%20Can't%20Claim%20Land%3A%20Waqf%20Changes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20opposition's%20proposals%20were%20rejected%20by%20a%2010%3A16%20vote%20after%20committee%20members%20voted%20on%20party%20lines%3B%20the%20JPC%20has%2016%20MPs%20from%20the%20BJP%20or%20allied%20parties%20and%20only%2010%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20to%20confirm%20acceptance%20of%20the%2014%20changes%20will%20take%20place%20January%2029%2C%20and%20the%20final%20report%20will%20be%20submitted%20by%20January%2031%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20had%20originally%20been%20asked%20to%20file%20the%20report%20by%20November%2029%20but%20that%20deadline%20was%20extended%20to%20February%2013%2C%20the%20final%20day%20of%20the%20Budget%20Session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChanges%20to%20the%20Waqf%20laws%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20earlier%2C%20are%20meant%20to%20empower%20Muslim%20women%20who%20%26quot%3Bsuffered%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20old%20law.%20However%2C%20critics%2C%20including%20Trinamool%20leader%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%2C%20and%20AIMIM%20boss%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20(both%20JPC%20members)%2C%20have%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20attack%20on%20freedom%20of%20religion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf