ults%3A%20The%20company%20had%20reported%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%20176.64%20crore%20during%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fadani-total-gas-q3-fy25-company-results-profit-revenue-shares-125012700644_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat%20Cost...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Turns%20Down%20Application%20In%20Hindenburg%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20upheld%20the%20Registry's%20order%20that%20refused%20to%20admit%20a%20petition%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20SEBI%20to%20submit%20a%20conclusive%20report%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20case.%20The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20R%20Mahadevan%20also%20asked%20how%20much%20cost%20should%20be%20imposed%20on%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Advocate%20Vishal%20Tiwari.%20Eventually%2C%20it%20dismissed%20the%20matter%20without%20imposing%20any%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20Hindenburg%20published%20a%20report%20targeting%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20accused%20the%20conglomerate%20of%20stock%20manipulation.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%2C%20mischievous%20and%20manipulative%20selections%20of%20publicly%20available%20information%26quot%3B%20to%20arrive%20at%20%26quot%3Bpredetermined%20conclusions%20for%20personal%20profiteering%20with%20wanton%20disregard%20for%20facts%20and%20the%20law%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20turned%20down%20petitions%2C%20including%20one%20by%20Mr%20Tiwari%2C%20seeking%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20against%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20ruling%20comes%20weeks%20after%20Hindenburg%20Research%20announced%20it%20was%20shutting%20down.%20The%20shock%20development%20has%20sparked%20speculation%20that%20the%20short%20seller%20is%20disbanding%20to%20avoid%20a%20possible%20India-US%20joint%20investigation%2C%20now%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20taken%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20registrar%20last%20year%2C%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI%20to%20submit%20its%20conclusive%20investigation%20report%20on%20Hindenburg's%20allegations%20against%20Adani%20Group.%20He%20also%20sought%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20short%20seller's%20allegations%20in%20its%20fresh%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Registrar%20rejected%20the%20application%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20issue%20had%20been%20addressed%20in%20the%20January%20ruling%20of%20the%20top%20court.%20Mr%20Tiwari%20then%20challenged%20the%20registrar's%20move.%20Today%2C%20the%20court%20upheld%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20July%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20dismissed%20a%20review%20petition%20filed%20against%20its%20earlier%20verdict%20refusing%20to%20form%20any%20SIT%20to%20probe%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20detailed%20order%20on%20January%203%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20reports%20prepared%20by%20third-party%20organisations%20such%20as%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20and%20Hindenburg%20Research%20could%20not%20be%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Bconclusive%20proof%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20said%20the%20reliance%20placed%20by%20petitioners%20on%20newspaper%20articles%20or%20reports%20by%20third-party%20organisations%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20inspire%20confidence%26quot%3B%20to%20question%20SEBI's%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737969720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.co