d%20is%20said%20to%20be%20raising%20a%20further%20%24200%20million%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoice-cloning-startup-elevenlabs-raising-funding-valuation-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20first%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecent%20breakthroughs%20in%20real-time%20speech-to-speech%20processing%20have%20unlocked%20new%20use%20cases%2C%20including%20virtual%20assistants%2C%20customer%20support%2C%20and%20voice-based%20productivity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sivesh%20Sukumar%2C%20an%20investor%20at%20VC%20firm%20Balderton.%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20like%20ElevenLabs%20and%20OpenAI%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20space%2C%20with%20ElevenLabs%20releasing%20a%20real-time%20API%20expected%20to%20drive%20further%20adoption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoice%20AI%20is%20a%20comparatively%20nascent%20space%2C%20so%20there%20isn't%20an%20established%20incumbent%20yet%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20triggering%20investor%20excitement%20for%20the%20untapped%20opportunities%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20Sukumar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b60e9894-06de-44be-a91b-c8fc0bdd3fcc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20expanding%20ecosystem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20are%20quickly%20identifying%20how%20to%20tailor%20voice%20technology%20to%20a%20host%20of%20enterprise%20and%20consumer%20needs.%20And%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagentic-ai-employees-ceos-managers-bots-davos-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagentic%20AI%20a%20hot%20topic%20for%20CEOs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20overlap%20with%20voice%20technology%20could%20hold%20high%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlayAI%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20is%20developing%20an%20AI%20platform%20for%20text-to-speech%20models%20and%20AI%20voice%20agents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechfundingnews.com%2Fplayai-generative-ai-human-like-speech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20%2421%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20seed%20funding%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20interest%20in%20building%20voice%20agents%2C%20which%20a%20human%20can%20speak%20to%20just%20like%20it's%20another%20human%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PlayAI%20cofounder%20Hammad%20Syed.%20%26quot%3BVoice%20AI%20is%20going%20mainstream%20and%20will%20be%20a%20key%20interface%20in%20how%20people%20interact%20with%20technology.%20Investors%20definitely%20realize%20this%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVCs%20scouring%20the%20ecosystem%20to%20make%20their%20next%20big%20bet%20are%20now%20looking%20at%20voice%20AI%20as%20a%20technology%20stack%2C%20said%20Steve%20Jang%2C%20founder%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20Kindred%20Ventures%2C%20which%20also%20backed%20PlayAI.%20The%20firm's%20investment%20thesis%20is%20to%20back%20startups%20%26quot%3Bwith%20multiple%20layers%20with%20many%20use%20cases%20in%20consumer%2C%20enterprise%2C%20and%20creativity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20there%20are%20specialized%20and%20foundational%20models.%20Second%2C%20there%20are%20infrastructure%20services%20and%20tools%2C%20which%20offer%20access%20and%20integration%20with%20these%20models.%20And%20then%2C%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20there%20is%20the%20vast%20vertical%20application%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sector%20is%20also%20attractive%20to%20investors%20because%20voice%20is%20an%20easy%20category%20to%20cash%20in%20on.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20price%20it%20by%20the%20outcome%2C%20so%20it's%20pretty%20easy%20to%20monetize%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jonathan%20Userovici%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20VC%20firm%20Headline.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20you%20have%20so%20much%20revenue%20traction%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20pretty%20easy%20to%20get%20a%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20replacing%20a%20human%20doing%20that%20labor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20appetite%20for%20voice%20AI%20has%20also%20skyrocketed.%20With%20more%20users%20preferring%20to%20take%20in%20information%20through%20audio%20formats%20like%20podcasts%2C%20Sukumar%20highlighted%20the%20growing%20consumer%20demand%20for%20voice%20control%20and%20audio%20interfaces.%20He%20built%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpersuasiondojo.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPersuAIsion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20voice%20AI%20platform%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20practice%20real-world%20conversations%20%E2%80%94%20from%20job%20interviews%20to%20first%20dates%20%E2%80%94%20because%20he%20saw%20the%20scope%20for%20voice%20to%20cater%20to%20such%20consumer%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20OpenAI%20can%20capture%20the%20consumer%20voice%20agent%2C%20they'll%20be%20what%20Siri%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20interfacing%20with%20personal%20devices%2C%20and%20there's%20just%20going%20to%20be%20better%20e-commerce%20consumer%20experience%20on%20that%20front.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259f52ab3-797d-41bf-b166-d8228ab6491f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrontier%20labs%20are%20catching%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20growing%20popularity%2C%20voice%20AI%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20have%20one%20established%20juggernaut%20just%20yet.%20Part%20of%20the%20reason%20could%20be%20that%20frontier%20labs%20have%20largely%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20space%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20a%20concern%20that%20a%20misuse%20of%20voice%20generation%20capabilities%20could%20result%20in%20a%20potential%20backlash%2C%20according%20to%20Air%20Street%20Capital's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stateof.ai%2F2024-report-launch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20State%20of%20AI%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20scraping%20huge%20quantities%20of%20audio%20and%20video%20data%2C%20frontier%20labs%20have%20been%20slow%20to%20release%20text-to-