t%20his%20actions%20are%20to%20protect%20America's%20%26quot%3Bsovereignty%26quot%3B%20and%20make%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Brespect%26quot%3B%20its%20authority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Colombia%20agreed%20to%20the%20unrestricted%20acceptance%20of%20%26quot%3Ball%20illegal%20aliens%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20White%20House%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday's%20events%20make%20clear%20to%20the%20world%20that%20America%20is%20respected%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20will%20continue%20to%20fiercely%20protect%20our%20nation's%20sovereignty%2C%20and%20he%20expects%20all%20other%20nations%20of%20the%20world%20to%20fully%20cooperate%20in%20accepting%20the%20deportation%20of%20their%20citizens%20illegally%20present%20in%20the%20United%20States.%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20whole%20economic%20warfare%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20even%20went%20ahead%20and%20shared%20a%20photo%20of%20himself%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20where%20he%20is%20seen%20wearing%20a%20fedora%20hat%20alongside%20a%20sign%20that%20read%20%26quot%3BFAFO.%26quot%3B%20The%20acronym%20is%20widely%20associated%20with%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3BF***%20around%2C%20find%20out%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20is%20often%20used%20as%20a%20warning%20that%20one's%20actions%20will%20have%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20awesome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWeWUeF17Gm%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWeWUeF17Gm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1883694908298625359%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2027%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20Global%20Relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20backing%20down%2C%20Mr%20Petro%20made%20sure%20to%20tell%20Donald%20Trump%20that%20he%20didn't%20like%20him%20or%20his%20policies%20on%20migration.%20In%20a%20lengthy%20response%20on%20X%2C%20he%20said%20Mr%20Trump%20would%20%26quot%3Bwipe%20out%20the%20human%20species%20because%20of%20greed%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20the%20US%20president%20of%20considering%20Colombians%20an%20%26quot%3Binferior%20race.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20describe%20himself%20as%20%26quot%3Bstubborn%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20while%20Mr%20Trump%20could%20try%20to%20%26quot%3Bcarry%20out%20a%20coup%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20strength%20and%20arrogance%26quot%3B%20he%20would%20fight%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20thousands%20of%20migrants%20from%20around%20the%20world%20enter%20the%20US%20after%20travelling%20up%20through%20Colombia%20across%20the%20Darien%20Gap%20-%20a%20key%20choke%20point%20just%20north%20of%20the%20Panama-Colombia%20border.%20The%20retaliatory%20measures%20by%20the%20US%20will%20no%20doubt%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20Mr%20Trump's%20administration%20to%20work%20with%20Colombia%20to%20stop%20this%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Petro%20alluded%20as%20much%20in%20his%20response%2C%20noting%20that%20if%20talks%20over%20managing%20migration%20through%20Darien%20were%20suspended%2C%20%26quot%3Billegal%20activities%20will%20increase%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20today%20on%2C%20Colombia%20is%20open%20to%20the%20entire%20world%2C%20with%20open%20arms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20what%20could%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20veiled%20threat%20of%20more%20undocumented%20migrants%20on%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20tariff%20threats%20to%20Columbia%2C%20the%20US%20is%20also%20witnessing%20diplomatic%20fallout%20from%20other%20Latin%20American%20nations.%20While%20Mexico%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20use%20of%20military%20planes%20for%20deportations%2C%20Brazil%20has%20expressed%20worries%20over%20the%20treatment%20of%20deported%20migrants%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20reportedly%20handcuffed%20during%20the%20flight%20out%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%20Threats%20Can%20Backfire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Mr%20Trump%20goes%20ahead%20with%20his%20tariff%20threats%2C%20his%20sanctions%20could%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%20for%20US%20consumers.%20The%20US%20imports%20about%2027%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20coffee%20from%20Colombia%20worth%20nearly%20%242bn%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture.%20It%20also%20imports%20other%20goods%20like%20bananas%2C%20crude%20oil%2C%20avocados%20and%20flowers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImporters%20could%20shift%20to%20other%20sources%20to%20avoid%20this%2C%20which%20would%20hit%20Colombian%20producers%20by%20reducing%20a%20key%20market%2C%20adding%20strain%20to%20an%20already%20fragile%20global%20trade%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737966360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fs1upjan8_trump_625x300_27_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcooperate-or-in-face-off-with-columbia-donald-trumps-strong-message-to-world-7569495%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Not%20even%20a%20week%20into%20his%20presidency%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20played%20his%20promised%20tariff%20card%20to%20navigate%20a%20complex%20diplomatic%20curve%20and%20drill%20home%20his%20'America%20first'%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcooperate-or-in-face-off-with-columbia-donald-trumps-strong-message-to-world-7569495%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bandra%20To%20Marine%20Drive%20In%2010%20Minutes%3A%20All%20About%20Mumbai's%20Coastal%20Road%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20north-bound%20bridge%20connecting%20Mumbai%20Coastal%20Road%20with%20the%20Bandra-Worli%20Sea%20Link%20has%20been%20opened%20for%20the%20public%20from%20Monday%2C%20easing%20travel%20issues%20on%20the%20congested%20roads%20of%20the%20city.%20Three%20interchanges%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20connectivity%20for%20vehicles%20moving%20to%20areas%20like%20Worli%2C%20Prabhadevi%2C%20Lower%20Parel%2C%20and%20Lotus%20Junction%2C%20were%20also%20inaugurated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge%20will%20remain%20open%20for%20use%20from%207%20am%20till%2012%20midnight%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20reduce%20travel%20time%20from%20Bandra%20to%20Marine%20Drive%20to%20around%2010%20to%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20Mumbai%20Coastal%20Road%20Project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWork%20on%20the%20Coastal%20Road%2C%20part%20of%20Mumbai's%20master%20plan%20from%201967%2C%20began%20in%202018.%20Though%20the%20project%20was%20slated%20to%20conclude%20by%202022%2C%20it%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic%2C%20among%20other%20reasons.%20It%20has%20so%20far%20cost%20Rs%2014%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20Coastal%20Road's%20first%20phase%20stretches%20over%2010.58%20km%2C%20connecting%20from%20the%20Princess%20Street%20Flyover%20at%20Marine%20Drive%20to%20the%20Worli%20end%20of%20the%20Bandra-Worli%20Sea%20Link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20layout%20of%204%2B4%20lanes%2C%20and%20the%20road%20has%20an%20array%20of%20modern%20infrastructure%20elements%2C%20including%20a%20bridge%20on%20stilts%2C%20an%20elevated%20road%2C%20and%20twin%20tunnels.%20The%20road%20has%20strategically%20placed%20interchanges%20at%20key%20locations%20such%20as%20Amarsons%20Garden%2C%20Haji%20Ali%20and%20Worli%20Seaface%20to%20make%20traffic%20flow%20smoother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20key%20features%20of%20the%20project%20is%20India's%20first%20undersea%20tunnel%2C%20one%20bound%20of%20which%20has%20been%20in%20use%20since%20March%202024.%20The%20twin%20tunnels%20with%20a%20diameter%20of%2012.19%20metres%20--%20only%20one%20side%20of%20which%20is%20currently%20open%20--%20run%2017%20to%2020%20meters%20below%20the%20sea%20level.%20The%202.07%20km%20tunnel%20begins%20near%20Girgaon%20(ahead%20of%20Marine%20Drive)%2C%20extends%20north%20under%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%20Girgaon%20Chowpatty%20and%20Malabar%20Hill%2C%20and%20end%20at%20Breach%20Candy's%20Priyadarshini%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20south-bound%20arm%20of%20Coastal%20Road%20opened%20from%20Worli%20to%20Marine%20Drive%20on%20March%2011.%20The%20north-bound%20arm%20opened%20from%20Marine%20Drive%20till%20Haji%20Ali%20on%20June%2010.%20Then%2C%20on%20July%2011%2C%20the%20stretch%20from%20Haji%20Ali%20to%20Worli%20became%20operational.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recently-inaugurated%20north-bound%20bridge%20is%20827%20metres%20long%2C%20with%20699%20metres%20over%20the%20sea%20and%20a%20128-metre%20access%20road.%20The%20bridge%20includes%20a%20143-metre%20long%2C%2027-metre%20wide%20and%2031-metre%20high%20'Bow%20Arch%20String%20Girder'%20weighing%20approximately%202%2C400%20metric%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2070%20hectares%20of%20green%20space%20will%20be%20created%2C%20where%20cycle%20tracks%2C%20public%20parks%2C%20jogging%20tracks%2C%20and%20open%20auditoriums%20will%20be%20built.%20This%20project%20will%20provide%20new%20recreational%20areas%20to%20Mumbaikars.%20Further%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20sea%20protection%20wall%20has%20also%20been%20proposed%20to%20prevent%20erosion%20and%20protect%20the%20project%20from%20high%20sea%20waves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20project%20spans%2020%20kilometres%20between%20Versova%20and%20Dahisar%20and%20it%20is%20under%20construction.%20The%20coastal%20road%20cuts%20down%20the%2045-minute%20commute%20from%20Girgaon%20to%20Worli%20to%20just%2010%20minutes.%20Further%2C%20the%20project%20also%20significantly%20reduces%20the%20travel%20time%20from%20south%20Mumbai%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2050%20lakh%20vehicles%20have%20used%20the%20coastal%20road%20route%20from%20March%2012%20to%20December%2031%2C%202024%2C%20with%20the%20daily%20average%20being%2018%2C000-20%2C000%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20said%20the%20coastal%20road%20will%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20fuel%20for%20Mumbaikars%20and%20will%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20getting%20rid%20of%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2094%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20work%20completed%2C%20the%20coastal%20road%20will%20be%20fully%20open%20to%20Mumbaikars%20upon%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20Prabhadevi%20connector%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737966300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ferc280ag_dharmaveer-swarajya-rakshak-chhatrapati-sambhaji-maharaj-mumbai-coastal-road_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fbandra-to-marine-drive-in-10-minutes-how-coastal-road-will-end-mumbai-traffic-issues-7569333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20north-bound%20bridge%20connecting%20Mumbai%20Coastal%20Road%20with%20the%20Bandra-Worli%20Sea%20Link%20has%20been%20opened%20for%20the%20public%2C%20easing%20travel%20issues%20on%20the%20congested%20roads%20of%20the%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fbandra-to-marine-drive-in-10-minutes-how-coastal-road-will-end-mumbai-traffic-issues-7569333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Third%20Act%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Personal%20Doc%20Is%20Both%20a%20Searing%20Historical%20Record%20and%20a%20Poignant%20Father-Son%20Narrative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737965728000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FThird-Act.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236286991%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20weight%2