o%20Christianity.%20The%20High%20Court%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20Baghels'%20insistence%20on%20burial%20at%20the%20village%20graveyard%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20Satish%20Chandra%20Sharma%20had%20earlier%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bpained%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20person%20had%20to%20come%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20his%20father's%20burial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20Baghel's%20lawyer%20Colin%20Gonsalves%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20family%20members%20were%20buried%20in%20the%20village%20burial%20ground%20even%20though%20they%20had%20converted.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20outside%20the%20village...%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20treated%20like%20an%20untouchable%20just%20because%20I%20converted.%26quot%3B%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20opposed%20this%20and%20said%20this%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmovement%26quot%3B%20that%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20disturbance%20between%20tribal%20Hindus%20and%20tribal%20Christians.%20%26quot%3BJust%2020%20km%20away%20there%20is%20a%20Christian%20burial%20ground.%20This%20ground%20is%20a%20Hindu%20tribal%20burial%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%20today%20said%20there%20were%20two%20judgments%20and%20went%20on%20to%20deliver%20hers.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20said%20that%20death%20is%20a%20great%20leveller%20and%20we%20need%20to%20remind%20ourselves%20of%20this.%20This%20death%20has%20led%20to%20divisiveness%20among%20villagers%20on%20the%20right%20to%20burial.%20The%20appellant%20says%20there%20is%20discrimination%20and%20prejudice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0Justice%20Nagarathna%20noted%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20accepted%20a%20suggestion%20that%20displaced%20the%20practices%20being%20followed%20in%20the%20village.%20%26quot%3BThe%20death%20of%20the%20person%20has%20given%20(way)%20to%20disahrmony%20since%20it%20was%20not%20solved%20by%20the%20village%20panchayat.%20Panchayat%20has%20been%20taking%20sides%20which%20led%20to%20the%20case%20in%20high%20court%20and%20Supreme%20Court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20pointed%20to%20the%20police%20affidavit%20that%20says%20a%20Christian%20convert%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20burial%20on%20the%20village%20grounds.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20unfortunate%20and%20violates%20Articles%2021%20and%2014%20and%20furthers%20discrimination%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20religion.%20The%20State%20cannot%20deny%20equality%20before%20the%20law.%20How%20could%20ASP%20Bastar%20give%20such%20an%20affidavit%20and%20what%20was%20the%20authority%3F%20it%20betrays%20the%20sublime%20principle%20of%20secularism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulling%20up%20the%20village%20panchayat%2C%20she%20said%20its%20attitude%20gave%20rise%20to%20hostile%20discrimination.%20%26quot%3BThe%20gram%20panchayat%20failed%20in%20its%20duty%20to%20provide%20burial%20which%20led%20to%20social%20ostracisation%20of%20appellant%20and%20his%20family.%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20directed%20that%20the%20burial%20be%20done%20on%20Baghels'%20private%20agricultural%20land.%20She%20also%20said%20the%20State%20must%20earmark%20a%20graveyard%20for%20Christians%20across%20all%20states%20within%20two%20months.%20But%2C%20Justice%20Sharma%20disagreed%20with%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sharma%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bunable%20to%20persuade%20myself%20to%20the%20directions%20issued%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fulcrum%20seems%20to%20boil%20down%20to%20whether%20fundamental%20rights%20to%20conduct%20religious%20burial%20ceremonies%20be%20extended%20to%20other%20places%20earmarked%20for%20other%20faiths%20in%20a%20blanket%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20designated%20burial%20ground%20is%20in%20Karakwal%2C%20just%2020%20km%20away.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20there%20should%20be%20an%20unqualified%20right%20to%20burial.%20Sweeping%20and%20illusionary%20rights%20can%20lead%20to%20public%20order%20disruption.%20Maintenance%20of%20public%20order%20is%20in%20the%20larger%20interest%20of%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Sharma%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20state%20administration%20must%20provide%20transport%20and%20security%20for%20the%20burial%20in%20the%20grounds%2020%20km%20from%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%20then%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20refer%20the%20matter%20to%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20since%20the%20body%20is%20in%20the%20morgue%20since%20Jan%207.%20We%20issue%20these%20directions%20under%20Article%20142%3A%201)%20The%20burial%20shall%20take%20place%20in%20the%20burial%20ground%20of%20Karakwal%202)%20All%20logistic%20support%20to%20be%20given.%20These%20directions%20are%20issues%20to%20allay%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20family%20of%20the%20deceased.%20Appeal%20disposed%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737960720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2Fvoni7s98_supreme-court-new_650x400_12_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-bv-nagarathna-justice-sc-sharma-body-in-morgue-for-3-weeks-supreme-court-clears-bastar-burial-roadblocks-7568634%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20delivered%20a%20split%20verdict%20in%20the%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20burial%20of%20a%20Christian%20pastor%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bastar%2C%20but%20did%20not%20refer%20the%20matter%20to%20a%20larger%20bench%20because%20the%20body%20has%20been%20in%20the%20morgue%20for%20nearly%20three%20weeks%20now%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-bv-nagarathna-justice-sc-sharma-body-in-morgue-for-3-weeks-supreme-court-clears-bastar-burial-roadblocks-7568634%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Words%20matter%2C%20and%20it%20is%20back%2