pists-who%20have%20illegally%20come%20into%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCriminals%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20hide%20in%20America's%20schools%20and%20churches%20to%20avoid%20arrest.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20will%20not%20tie%20the%20hands%20of%20our%20brave%20law%20enforcement%2C%20and%20instead%20trusts%20them%20to%20use%20common%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAction%20Draw%20Sikh%20Groups'%20Ire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20drew%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20some%20Sikh%20organisations%20which%20see%20such%20actions%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20sanctity%20of%20their%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Sikh%20American%20Legal%20Defence%20and%20Education%20Fund%20(SALDF)%20expressed%20grave%20concern%20over%20the%20directive%20rescinding%20the%20guidelines%20that%20designated%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%20areas%26quot%3B%2C%20such%20as%20houses%20of%20worship%2C%20where%20immigration%20enforcement%20actions%20were%20previously%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20troubling%20shift%20in%20policy%20comes%20in%20tandem%20with%20community%20reports%20of%20DHS%20agents%20visiting%20gurdwaras%20in%20the%20New%20York%20and%20New%20Jersey%20areas%20just%20days%20after%20the%20directive%20was%20issued%2C%26quot%3B%20SALDF%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20alarmed%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security's%20decision%20to%20eliminate%20protections%20for%20sensitive%20areas%20and%20then%20target%20places%20of%20worship%20like%20gurdwaras%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kiran%20Kaur%20Gill%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20SALDEF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20said%20gurdwaras%20are%20not%20just%20places%20of%20worship%3B%20they%20are%20vital%20community%20centres%20that%20provide%20support%2C%20nourishment%2C%20and%20spiritual%20solace%20to%20Sikhs%20and%20the%20broader%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTargeting%20these%20spaces%20for%20enforcement%20actions%20threatens%20the%20sanctity%20of%20our%20faith%20and%20sends%20a%20chilling%20message%20to%20immigrant%20communities%20nationwide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESikh%20Coalition%20said%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20decision%20to%20rescind%20the%20DHS%20policy%20on%20%26quot%3Bprotected%20areas%26quot%3B%20(which%20also%20included%20hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20social%20service%20providers%2C%20and%20more)%20opens%20the%20door%20to%20Immigrations%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20agents%20conducting%20surveillance%2C%20investigations%2C%20arrests%2C%20and%20raids%20at%20gurdwaras.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20our%20gurdwaras%20could%20be%20subject%20to%20government%20surveillance%20and%20raids%20by%20armed%20law%20enforcement%20with%20or%20without%20warrants%20is%20unacceptable%20to%20the%20Sikh%20faith%20tradition.%20It%20will%20burden%20religious%20exercise%20by%20limiting%20the%20ability%20of%20Sikhs%20to%20gather%20and%20associate%20with%20one%20another%20in%20accordance%20with%20our%20faith%2C%26quot%3B%20Sikh%20Coalition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20harkens%20to%20dark%20periods%20in%20our%20collective%20memory%20when%20governments%20interfered%20in%20the%20ability%20of%20Sikhs%20to%20practice%20our%20faith%20freely-with%20deadly%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Sikhs-whether%20documented%20or%20undocumented-are%20concerned%20with%20gurdwara%20raids%20and%20surveillance%2C%20gurdwaras%20may%20well%20be%20impacted%20by%20decreased%20attendance%2C%20and%20thus%20an%20inability%20to%20carry%20out%20essential%20religious%20practices%20in%20a%20meaningful%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sikh%20Coalition.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737959940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.n