al-of-a-13-year-old-girl-separated-from-her-family-13294967%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Women%20in%20UP%20%26amp%3B%20Bihar%20Are%20Defying%20Widowhood%2C%20Violence%2C%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Climate%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20shatter%20barriers%2C%20question%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20and%20inspire%20a%20wave%20of%20change%3F%20For%20countless%20women%20across%20India%20running%20small%20grassroots%20organisations%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mix%20of%20courage%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20an%20unshakable%20urge%20to%20address%20deep-rooted%20inequities%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20progress%20has%20been%20made%2C%20gender%20equality%20remains%20elusive.%20Women%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20and%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20continue%20to%20face%20entrenched%20barriers%20such%20as%20gender-based%20violence%2C%20social%20exclusion%2C%20and%20limited%20access%20to%20resources.%20At%20the%20current%20pace%2C%20it%20will%20take%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fpress%2F2023%2F06%2Fgender-equality-is-stalling-131-years-to-close-the-gap%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E131%20years%20to%20achieve%20gender%20parity%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%20But%20this%20can%20change%20when%20women%20begin%20to%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMarriage%2C%20separation%2C%20and%20widowhood%20in%20rural%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20grassroots%2C%20early%20marriage%2C%20motherhood%2C%20widowhood%2C%20divorce%20or%20separation%20can%20be%20defining%20milestones%20for%20women%3B%20stepping%20away%20from%20the%20norm%20and%20reconstructing%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20identity%20post%20widowhood%20or%20separation%20is%20often%20an%20act%20of%20bold%20agency%2C%20and%20is%20pivotal%20for%20women%20working%20and%20enduring%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%20often%20having%20to%20relive%20personal%20trauma%20while%20supporting