ron-rich%20food%2C%20such%20as%20jaggery%20and%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20and%20iron%20tablets.%20My%20haemoglobin%20was%2010%20%5Bnormal%20range%20is%2012.0-15.5%20g%2FdL%5D.%20I%20followed%20all%20the%20instructions%20and%20my%20baby%20was%20born%20a%20month%20back.%20Both%20of%20us%20are%20healthy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20provide%20much-needed%20diagnostic%20services%20to%20underserved%20populations%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Dibyajyoti%20Parida%20IAS%20spearheaded%20the%20Nirikhyana%20initiative%20in%20Ganjam%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceptualised%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20programme%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20glaring%20gap%20in%20access%20to%20essential%20diagnostic%20services%2C%20especially%20ultrasounds%20for%20pregnant%20women%2C%20in%20remote%20villages.%20Formally%20launched%20in%202023%2C%20this%20service%20has%20significantly%20improved%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F45181%2Ftribal-women-india-odisha-maternal-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernal%20and%20child%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20providing%20reassurance%20to%201.38%20lakh%20pregnant%20women%2C%20including%20Jhili%2C%20during%20a%20vulnerable%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBridging%20the%20diagnostic%20gap%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20extensive%20field%20visits%20and%20review%20meetings%20after%20his%20joining%20in%20July%202022%2C%20Dibyajyoti%20found%20a%20critical%20lack%20of%20ultrasound%20facilities%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20gap%20left%20many%20pregnant%20women%20without%20access%20to%20the%20necessary%20ultrasounds%20duri