ement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDibyajyoti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20structured%20three-tier%20system%20approach%20allows%20for%20the%20proactive%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325599%2Fmadurai-jiovio-healthcare-startup-pregnancy-risk-monitoring-device-rural-women-infant-mortality%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentification%20of%20high-risk%20pregnancies%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20least%2020%20to%2025%20days%20before%20the%20due%20date.%20This%20allows%20us%20to%20enable%20timely%20interventions%20and%20treatment%20that%20significantly%20help%20us%20reduce%20maternal%20deaths%2C%20still-births%2C%20and%20child%20mortality%20rates%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUltrasounds%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20%E2%80%98rich%20person%E2%80%99s%20thing%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20groundbreaking%20aspect%20of%20the%20initiative%20is%20making%20ultrasounds%20free.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20patriarchal%20society%2C%20spending%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%20is%20often%20considered%20a%20burden.%20Rural%20women%20felt%20that%20ultrasound%20scans%20were%20a%20luxury%20reserved%20for%20the%20rich.%20We%20made%20it%20free%20to%20address%20this%20policy%20gap%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Dheenah%2C%20adding%20that%20in%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group%20(PVTG)%20areas%2C%20free%20transportation%20is%20provided%20to%20ensure%20women%20can%20access%20healthcare%20without%20financial%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUtilising%20existing%20resources%20from%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%2C%20district%20mineral%20funds%2C%20and%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20(CSR)%20budgets%2C%20the%20project%20effectively%20covers